parameters:
In the expanding darkness, no matter how much I ran or fought, I
gritted my teeth at the complete lack of response to that eerie
feeling.

Like a bug being toyed with in the palm of a hand... I... Ah, I feel
like trembling, as if my very existence is different. The lifeless
gaze looks down on me, as if I'm being sucked into it...

I want my body, my womb, to be degraded and entrusted to that palm...
To shake off that desire, I spit it out.

Contrary to my strong words, my knees tremble, and my body, dripping
with love juices, is... my body...
I stood up again and made it this far.

However, my body, which was thoroughly toyed with in their palm and
dragged down to the depths of depravity, is now even more terrified
than before. The trembling of my legs and the pulsation of my womb
won't stop. It continues to overflow with love juices without end.
Stand up and face it with courage
Bowing my head and seeking mercy

......If I hang my head here, it will truly--truly--end here. I can never go
back. Never--never--absolutely. Forever. Eternally.
